AISDB: Readme
=============

.. image:: https://git-dev.cs.dal.ca/meridian/aisdb/badges/master/pipeline.svg

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/gitlab/coverage/meridian/aisdb/master?gitlab_url=https%3A%2F%2Fgit-dev.cs.dal.ca&job_name=python-test

